  <brief_title>Psychological Assessment of Adults Seeking Orthodontic Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of Personality Characteristics and Self-esteem on the Relationship Between Orthodontic Treatment Need and Oral-health Related Quality of Life in Adults.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
